[Patient] "What foods should I eat to help manage my heart failure?"
[Healthcare Educator] "Focus on fruits, veggies, whole grains, lean proteins, and limit sodium."
[Patient] "Can I still enjoy my favorite foods like fried chicken and macaroni and cheese?"
[Healthcare Educator] "Try baked or grilled chicken and whole grain pasta for heart-healthy versions."
[Patient] "I love soul food. How can I make it healthier?"
[Healthcare Educator] "Use less salt, bake instead of fry, and add more veggies to traditional dishes."
[Patient] "I often eat out at restaurants. Any tips for making healthier choices?"
[Healthcare Educator] "Look for grilled or steamed options, ask for sauces on the side, and choose smaller portions."